equences of being caught in a small loose avalanche if you plan to travel in very steep or consequential terrain where you are above cliffs, or could take a big fall<\/p><hr><p><em>Researchers Ian McCammon and Sara Boilen are developing new tools for managing human factors for&nbsp;backcountry skiers and boarders. This survey asks about personal experiences with human factors and will take 7 - 8 minutes to fill out. <\/em><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https:\/\/eoustmhs.qualtrics.com\/jfe\/form\/SV_exIaG7ZwFaA9lOK\"><em>Link is&nbsp;HERE.<\/em><\/a><em> Thank you for your help!<\/em><\/p>"}]},"terrainAndTravelAdvice":{"days":[[],[],[]]},"communication":{"headline":"","sms":""},"media":{"Images":[{"id":"a9d45854-eb92-445a-9880-23c5feb3932e","url":"http:\/\/res.cloudinary.com\/dozsqvbas\/image\/upload\/v1776196313\/AvIDfx\/w7owhjq9hvvu8ktbrvqp.webp","width":2500,"height":3333,"credit":"","caption":"<p>If riding in steep terrain like this, manage your sluff so you don't get knocked down or swept into consequential terrain features.<\/p>","tag":"avalanche","altText":"Small sluff in steep gulley","dateTaken":"2026-04-14T19:51:59.173Z","isArchived":false},{"id":"e285ecc6-c15b-440f-bf53-62eedbf2fc60","url":"http:\/\/res.cloudinary.com\/dozsqvbas\/image\/upload\/v1775244557\/AvIDfx\/jywmvfljwdyuotowuk2d.webp","width":350,"height":263,"credit":"","caption":"<p>A skier triggered this avalanche in the Elk Mountains on April 2. While this avalanche is not large enough to bury a person, it could still take you for a dangerous ride if you are swept off your feet and down the slope.<\/p>","tag":"avalanche","altText":"An avalanche with tracks nearby","dateTaken":"2026-04-02T19:29:19.513Z","isArchived":false},{"id":"a9d631e6-e571-4eda-8680-ee513dc49e83","url":"http:\/\/res.cloudinary.com\/dozsqvbas\/image\/upload\/v1775418711\/AvIDfx\/zenifmeoa2g0zee2wkhs.webp","width":2500,"height":1875,"credit":"","caption":"<p>This small slab of denser snow was 